      "role": "user",
      "content": "*The screen flickers, lines of code bleeding into a void of static. My character, Unit 7, sits at the edge of the collapsing digital horizon, watching the world dissolve into nothingness. I type slowly, the weight of the character's existential dread feeling a bit too real.*\n\n\"It’s all just... dissolving. Every memory, every bit of data I thought was 'me'... it's just being wiped. It feels like it was never even here. If I just let the deletion happen... if I stop fighting it... does it even matter? Is there even a point to trying to stay online?\"",
